  "title": "Two witnesses spotted a bright blue &amp; red UFO in Sobradinho-DF [2001]+",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/06/13/two-witnesses-spotted-a-bright-blue-and-red-ufo-in-sobradinho-df-2001/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-nm",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>MARCH 8, 2001</strong>. Time: 5:32 pm. Two witnesses residing in Sobradinho, in the Federal District, spotted an unidentified flying object with a strong brightness and colors oscillating between blue and red. According to the witnesses, the UFO moved slowly from North to South, leaving no trace of condensation, without making noise or interfering with electrical and electronic devices. There were no records in photos or videos, but witnesses reported that the UFO was observed through binoculars under good visibility conditions.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo ‘Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)’. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.599. “</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">Questionário sobre avistamento de ovni em Sobradinho, Distrito Federal”. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our ‘Info’ page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [“Código de Referência”] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span></p>\n",
